headline: 4 Electric Power Stocks to Consider Amid Industry Weaknesses
summary: Despite near-term weakness in the electric power industry, utilities like VST, EXC, ETR and AEE are set to benefit from their systematic investments, which allow them to serve their customers efficiently.
